15#define SINGLE_PRECISION
16#include "fp_lib.h"
17typedef su_int fixuint_t;
18#include "fp_fixuint_impl.inc"
19
20ARM_EABI_FNALIAS(f2uiz, fixunssfsi)
21
22COMPILER_RT_ABI su_int
23__fixunssfsi(fp_t a) {
24 return __fixuint(a);
25}
